# =============================================================================
# FRONTEND DEVELOPMENT NOTES (NEW - v0.10.0)
# =============================================================================

# Component development with mock data produces various debugging artifacts
# that should not be committed. The frontend architecture uses:
# - Mock data for UI development (tracked in components)
# - API integration points (tracked for backend connectivity)
# - CSS custom properties for theming (tracked in globals.css)
# - TypeScript interfaces (tracked with components)
#
# Frontend testing generates temporary files that should be excluded
# while keeping the core component architecture and styling in version control.

# =============================================================================
# DATABASE & CATEGORY SYSTEM NOTES (NEW - v0.10.0)
# =============================================================================

# The standardized 8-category system migration creates various backup and
# debug files that should not be committed. The category system includes:
# - Database schema updates (tracked via migration scripts)
# - Category metadata with visual identity (stored in database)
# - Frontend API integration (tracked in component code)
# - A/B testing compatibility (tracked in prompts.yaml)
#
# Migration artifacts and debug files are excluded while keeping
# the migration scripts and configuration in version control.

# =============================================================================
# DUAL STORAGE ARCHITECTURE NOTES
# =============================================================================

# SQLite database files excluded but schema tracked in:
# - database_setup.py (initial schema creation)
# - database_migration.py (schema evolution scripts)
# - migrate_categories.py (category standardization)
# - services/database_service.py (auto-creation logic)
#
# Google Sheets integration configured via:
# - .env file (GOOGLE_SHEETS_ID)
# - gsheetapi_credentials.json (excluded service account)
# - services/sheets_service.py (schema mapping)
#
# Frontend integration configured via:
# - globals.css (color system)
# - component TypeScript interfaces (tracked)
# - API endpoint integration (tracked in components)


